    dc:title "Review of the effusus group of the Lanternfly genus Pyrops Spinola, 1839, with one new species and notes on trophobiosis (Hemiptera: Fulgoromorpha: Fulgoridae)" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3785163>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3785173>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3785167>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3785165> ;
